{"tid":471288,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你估一部電話賺你好多咩？但求打個和","createTime":"2017-11-17T06:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T07:13:29.000Z","uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eb2c431dd6950463a50a024f568e441f30643933","tid":471288,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T06:26:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://buzzorange.com/techorange/2017/11/17/hiroshima-chair-apple-park/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Ftechorange%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2Fhiroshima-chair-apple-park%2F&d=BMeVM3TIdM2uoKT7xN9I%2B2Mi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=4e72cef3\" target=\"_blank\">https://buzzorange.com/techorange/2017/11/17/hiroshima-chair-apple-park/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/142239_d669ae32cfcc94fd9d23c89691725e27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F142239_d669ae32cfcc94fd9d23c89691725e27.jpg&h=2e7c9a1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作為蘋果其中一樣最矚目的「產品」，Apple Park 裡選用的產品都非常精緻。<br />\n<br />\nifanr 主編曾帶大家到賈伯斯劇院裡轉了一圈，見識了劇院裡由義大利公司 Poltrona Frau 生產的，每張造價高達 14000 美元（折合台幣 52 萬）的真皮座椅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/142348_d24203c3825979cb04cb68a48082ccd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F142348_d24203c3825979cb04cb68a48082ccd9.jpg&h=94859ff3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/142349_5ddb73b07da0b5f53d6f32b21f52527a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F142349_5ddb73b07da0b5f53d6f32b21f52527a.jpg&h=4ae2a34a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而在 辦公室領域 ，為了讓員工可以隨時停下來進行即興討論，蘋果在走道旁零散地安置了美國設計師 Eero Saarinen 設計的經典椅子 Womb Chair，每張價格約為 3900 美元。<br />\n<br />\n員工可以坐在零散分佈於走道旁的 Womb Chair 上，一邊聊天一邊欣賞戶外的景色。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/142441_bc9554d8a2f470c81111e0ab9579997b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F142441_bc9554d8a2f470c81111e0ab9579997b.jpg&h=67bd134c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遺憾在於，無論是賈伯斯劇院還是辦公領域，它們都不對遊客開放。因此，即使去到 Apple Park，也見不著這些由蘋果精心挑選的椅子。<br />\n<br />\n不過，對於有前往參觀計劃的讀者而言，將於 11 月 17 日正式開放的 Apple Park 訪客中心也有一款非常值得細心留意的產品，那就是這些看起來平凡無奇，卻比你的 iPhone X 還貴的廣島椅（Hiroshima chair）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/142519_d0c15038475e9c2c1b529a5ec5dcabc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F142519_d0c15038475e9c2c1b529a5ec5dcabc3.jpg&h=7b74c8e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37076be53ba0b9858af00883a8d91960a4f8c3dc","tid":471288,"uid":73731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T07:13:29.000Z","msg":"mphone 爆炸 不了"}]}